thread.title: Lincoln Tunnel Bus Crash Leaves 32 Injured

author: Zolan Kanno-Youngs
title: Lincoln Tunnel Bus Crash Leaves 32 Injured

organizations.name: lincoln tunnel bus crash leaves 32 injured two nj transit

text:
Two NJ Transit buses collided in the Lincoln Tunnel in Manhattan on Friday morning causing dozens of injuries, officials said.
The rear-end collision injured 32 people, including seven who suffered serious injuries, according to a Fire Department of New York spokeswoman.
